    {
      "id": "write_op", "type": "rectangle", "x": 60, "y": 200, "width": 420, "height": 90,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#2f9e44", "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a7",
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 8001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 8002,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"id": "t_write", "type": "text"}],
      "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_write", "type": "text", "x": 65, "y": 208, "width": 410, "height": 75,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a7a", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 8003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 8004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Writer (producer) — single thread only\n\n1. Check write_available() = capacity - (tail - head)\n2. If enough space: memcpy data at tail position\n3. Advance tail: tail.store(new_tail, release)\n   Release fence ensures data is visible before tail moves",
      "originalText": "Writer (producer) — single thread only\n\n1. Check write_available() = capacity - (tail - head)\n2. If enough space: memcpy data at tail position\n3. Advance tail: tail.store(new_tail, release)\n   Release fence ensures data is visible before tail moves",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "write_op", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "read_op", "type": "rectangle", "x": 60, "y": 310, "width": 420, "height": 90,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#c92a2a", "backgroundColor": "#ffe3e3",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a8",
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 9001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 9002,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"id": "t_read", "type": "text"}],
      "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_read", "type": "text", "x": 65, "y": 318, "width": 410, "height": 75,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a8a", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 9003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 9004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Reader (consumer) — single thread only\n\n1. Check read_available() = tail - head\n2. If data available: read from head position\n3. Advance head: head.store(new_head, release)\n   Release fence ensures read is complete before head moves",
      "originalText": "Reader (consumer) — single thread only\n\n1. Check read_available() = tail - head\n2. If data available: read from head position\n3. Advance head: head.store(new_head, release)\n   Release fence ensures read is complete before head moves",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "read_op", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "props_band", "type": "rectangle", "x": 540, "y": 80, "width": 340, "height": 340,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "#edf2ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 30, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a9",
